Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait compared to Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait compared to Accepted + Wait - Vendor
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait compared to Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait in cases that eventually reach Completed + In Call versus cases that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Wait when it appears in variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait grouped by resource
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Time from the start of the case to the execution of Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time between the preceding activity and Accepted + Wait when Completed + In Call occurs later in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait in variants that end with Completed + Resolved versus those that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + Wait to be done after Queued + Awaiting Assignment in traces that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total waiting time to the Accepted + Wait activity when the subsequent path leads to Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + Resolved in variants that also feature Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Wait in low-performance variants (performance > 1,000,000) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
